{"tid":2413894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國議員向國會再提防止台灣遭侵略法案","createTime":"2021-02-19T04:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T04:49:43.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7875168c990762bcbe3623cc74e5d52854481a","tid":2413894,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:50:41.000Z","msg":"美國議員向國會再提防止台灣遭侵略法案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=424571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424571&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69GCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=9e991cf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424571&h=bff8085d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=424571</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">美國兩名共和黨議員，向國會重提《防止台灣遭侵略法案》，授權美國總統在必要時動武防衛台灣。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨籍參議員斯科特和眾議員雷申塔勒，分別在參眾兩院提出《防止台灣遭侵略法案》，旨在進一步加強美國與台灣的關係，以及增強台灣抵禦大陸軍事行動的能力。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n法案內容包括，強化美國對台灣的長期政策，授權總統出於保護台灣，免受武裝攻擊的特定目的，有限度使用武力。法案亦要求大陸放棄使用或威脅使用武力實現兩岸統一，並且鼓勵美國總統和國務卿訪台，與台灣的總統會面，以及歡迎台灣的總統對美國國會聯席會議發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">另外，近40名跨黨派議員在眾議院提出另一項法案，要求協助台灣重獲世衛觀察員身份。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7d4d296413bd707555efcfd78d45a2002fd2ca45","tid":2413894,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"跨黨派議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拜登會唔會用行政命令取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7d1ab1fd1be4a6246500d00e17b14f9a4ab30b","tid":2413894,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b02cfabb666bc9c5c76ac2e224f1c1f1ac51af","tid":2413894,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83381b5e27380c3fa599a8e58883a2ba357f971d","tid":2413894,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}